sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Dev as User (VS Code)
    participant Ext as VS Code Extension
    participant API as Backend API (Render)
    participant DB as Supabase (DB & Storage)
    participant Q as Redis Queue (Upstash)
    participant Worker as Worker Node (Local/Cloud)

    Dev->>Ext: Clicks "Scan Local Code"
    Ext->>Ext: Zips code (Ignores node_modules)

    Note over Ext,API: POST /api/scans/upload
    Ext->>API: Uploads payload.zip

    API->>DB: Saves Zip to Storage and Creates Scan (Status PENDING)
    API->>Q: Pushes Job Ticket to Queue
    API-->>Ext: Returns 202 Accepted + scan_id

    loop Every 5 Seconds
        Note over Ext,API: GET /api/scans/{scan_id}
        Ext->>API: Is it done yet
        API-->>Ext: Status SCANNING
    end

    Q->>Worker: Pulls Job Ticket
    Worker->>DB: Downloads payload.zip
    Note right of Worker: Runs Scan Engine and LangGraph Agents

    Worker->>API: Webhook Sends Final Verified Bugs
    API->>DB: Updates Scan Status to COMPLETED and Saves Bugs

    Ext->>API: Is it done yet
    API-->>Ext: Status COMPLETED with Bug List Payload
    Ext->>Dev: Displays Bugs and Applies Patch in Editor